```{r}
library(tidyverse)
library(p8105.datasets)
library(plotly)
data("instacart")
instacart |> 
  janitor::clean_names()
```

```{r}
instacart |>
  mutate() |> 
  plot_ly(
    x = ~aisle, y = ~order_hour_of_day, type = "scatter", mode = "markers", alpha = 0.5)

```
